dvol - dynamic sound
====================
dvol is sound manage util for dwm.


Requirements
------------
In order to build dvol you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dvol is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dvol
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dvol
-------------
See the man page for details.
